  "texts": [
    "The last five epochs of the fine-tuned model were then used to generate 256K molecules (51,200 designs per each T value, ranging from 1.0 to 2.0 with a step of 0.25).",
    "The designs were ranked and filtered via log-likelihood score (Eq.",
    "(5)) and scaffold similarity to the training set (see \"Materials and methods\" for further details).",
    "The ten top-scoring molecules (1-10, Fig. 5a and Table 3) were considered for further characterization using MD simulations.",
    "As a reference for evaluation, we performed MD simulations also for the closest fine-tuning neighbor of the considered designs (compounds 11-16, selected based on scaffold similarity; Fig. 5a and Table 3)."
  ],
